msgid "Empty Map"
msgstr "Malplena Mapo"

msgid "Empty maps are not useful as maps, but they can be stacked and turned to maps which can be used."
msgstr ""
"Malplenaj mapoj ne estas utilaj kiel mapoj, sed oni povas stakigi ilin kaj "
"transformi ilin en uzeblajn mapojn."

msgid "Rightclick to create a filled map (which can't be stacked anymore)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Map"
msgstr "Mapo"

msgid "Shows a map image."
msgstr ""

msgid "When created, the map saves the nearby area as an image that can be viewed any time by holding the map."
msgstr ""

msgid "Hold the map in your hand. This will display a map on your screen."
msgstr ""
